title: Raum - Event Of Your Leaving (320kbps)
description:
This is a drone record. It is a collaboration between the popular drone artist Grouper (Liz Harris) and the lesser known Jefre Cantu-Ledesma. It's really very good, I'm sad that a lot of people missed out on it, so that's why I'm uploading it now. Enjoy :-)
